N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1155.3 - Designated areas

State Regulations

Cleaning, maintaining and repairing any aircraft, watercraft
or motor vehicle shall be accomplished only in areas designated, if any, for
that purpose by the manager. Notes
